data.description: Must see this beautiful open floor plan home featuring a main level master suite with soaking tub & updated shower.  Downstairs offers an open living space with updated flooring/carpet, add'l 1/2 bath, an office/sitting room, utility room and spacious foyer. Two bedrooms, full bath and a large bonus room or 4th bedroom upstairs, a perfect game room option. Fully fenced backyard with landscaping, 8x10 shed and UG sprinklers, covered patio and 3 car garage to store all your toys or extra storage space.
